						<term>aer compressus</term>
						</index> videndumque an ille eodem sese tempore restituat<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tempus restitutionis</term>
						</index> utcunque sit compressus, plus vel minus. Et fortasse generaliter verum est <anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_turbatio-1"/><app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">eandem potentiam utcunque turbatam<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>potentia turbata</term>
							</index></lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">eandem</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> vim turbata<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>vis turbata</term>
							</index> </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> potentiam utcunque turbatam <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> sese eodem tempore restituere,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tempus restitutionis</term>
						</index> sive plus sive minus turbata sit, et omnia gravia,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>grave</term>
						</index> nisi quid aliud intercurrat[,] eodem tempore ad centrum terrae<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>centrum terrae</term>
						</index> <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">perventura. Itaque tempora restitutionum<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>tempus restitutionis</term>
							</index> ut potentias<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>potentia turbata</term>
							</index> esse.</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">perventura.</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> Itaque </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> Itaque tempora ut potentias esse </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="3"> Itaque tempora <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/> potentias esse. <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> Hoc tam generale principium<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>principium generale</term>
						</index> meretur demonstrari. Si tamen Elaterium pondere<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_turbatio-2"/><index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>pondus onerans</term>
						</index> one-</p>
					<figure rendition="#own-line_centered" xml:id="Ch1.p11"><graphic url="../gesamttex/edit_VIII,3/images/LH_37_01_016_d1.svg" width="277.5168pt" xml:id="Ch1.p11.g1"/><head rendition="#c">[<hi rendition="#i">Fig. 1</hi>]</head></figure>
					<p rendition="#noindent" xml:id="Ch1.p12">retur[,] non eodem tempore restituetur<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tempus restitutionis</term>
						</index> valde compressum ac parum compressum,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>elaterium compressum</term>
						</index> nam extraneum aliquid praeterea agendum est magis in uno quam in altero. Hinc jam aeris resistentia<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>resistentia aeris</term>
						</index> et ipsum pondus chordae<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>pondus chordae</term>
						</index> efficient ut non sit perfectus isochronismus.<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>isochronismus restitutionis</term>
						</index></p>
					<p xml:id="Ch1.p13">Celeritas<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_isochr-1"/><index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>celeritas restitutionis</term>
						</index> determinatur tum a nisu<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>nisus restitutionis</term>
						</index> seu potentia agente,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>potentia agens</term>
						</index> tum a resistentia rei movendae.<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>resistentia rei movendae</term>
						</index> Sed si ab hac abstrahamus animum;<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>animus</term>
						</index> patet celeritates<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>celeritas restitutionis</term>
						</index> esse temporibus<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tempus restitutionis</term>
						</index> reciproce proportionales, ergo tempora reciproce proportionalia nisibus; nisus autem sunt in composita ratione potentiarum et turbationum,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>turbatio</term>
						</index> et nisus<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>nisus restitutionis</term>
						</index> ejusdem potentiae<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>potentia agens</term>
						</index> in ratione turbationum. Ergo tempora<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tempus restitutionis</term>
						</index> in reciproca ratione turbationum, sed cum turbationes<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>turbatio</term>
						</index> quovis momento<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>momentum temporis</term>
						</index> <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">immutentur, et</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">immutentur,</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> imo </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> et <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> eo minor sit nisus<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>nisus restitutionis</term>
						</index> sequens quo praecedens major fuit, hinc progressio per curvam exprimenda<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>progressio per curvam exprimenda</term>
						</index> erit, <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">et <ref><pb type="L"/><fw type="folNum">[16 v<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>]</fw></ref> res</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">et</note>
						<rdg wit="#L"><ref><pb type="L"/><fw type="folNum">[16 v<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>]</fw></ref> <note type="editorial">|</note> et <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">streicht Hrsg.</hi> |</note> res <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> eo redibit, ut ostendatur, eandem temporum<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tempus restitutionis</term>
						</index> summam esse. Moles gravium<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>moles gravium</term>
						</index> nihil obstabit, quominus eodem tempore ad centrum terrae<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>centrum terrae</term>
						</index> perveniant, quia ipsa eorum moles est causa turbationis.<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016v_isochr-2"/><index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>causa turbationis</term>
						</index> Videndum an dimidia chorda<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>chorda dimidia</term>
						</index> iisdem servatis duplo celerius vibret. Et sic videtur. Nam si tantundem tendatur quantum integra, erit duplo magis tensa<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>chorda tensa</term>
						</index> seu vim<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>vis tendens</term>
						</index> <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">passa[,] <app type="Cfootnote" from="#LH_37_01_016v_utcunque-1" to="#LH_37_01_016v_utcunque-2">
							<lem type="main"/>
							<note type="lemma-abbrev">utcunque <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/> modo</note>
							<note type="editorial">Leibniz meint hier wohl nicht mehr die Spannkraft, sondern die Auslenkung der Saite (<hi rendition="#i">pulsatio</hi>).</note>
							</app>utcunque autem tendatur semper<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016v_utcunque-1"/></lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">passa</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> . Ergo </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> semper </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="3"> utcunque autem tendatur semper <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> vibrat eodem modo. Videretur ergo corpus Elasticum<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016v_utcunque-2"/><index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>corpus elasticum</term>
						</index> omne quanto est minus, <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">eo vibrare celerius.</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">eo</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> fortius vibrare </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> vibrare celerius. <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> Etiam aerem ordinarium<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>aer ordinarius</term>
						</index> unius pedis cubici<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>pes cubicus</term>
						</index> fortius vibrare quam aerem duorum pedum cubicorum. Quod rursus mirabile est.<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_abschnitt_2-2"/></p>
					<p xml:id="Ch1.p14">Sonus<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_abschnitt_3-1"/><index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>sonus</term>
						</index> igitur pendet a partibus<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>pars aeris</term>
						</index> in quas aer vibratione<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>vibratio aeris</term>
						</index> quasi dissilit, et quae et ipsae vibrant et vicinas excitant, nam quo minores illae, hoc sonus <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">acutior.<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>sonus acutus</term>
							</index> Modus quo</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">acutior.</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> Cum ab vi </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> Modus quo <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> aer dissilit[,] hic esse videtur: chorda<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>chorda vibrans</term>
						</index> <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">vibrans circumjacentem aerem<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>aer circumjacens</term>
							</index> impellendo comprimit, is<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>aer compressus</term>
							</index></lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">vibrans</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> imprimit aer </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> circumjacentem aerem <app>
							<rdg wit="#L" n="a">premit et comprimit </rdg>
							<rdg wit="#L" n="b">impellendo comprimit, <app>
								<rdg wit="#L" n="aa">itaque </rdg>
								<rdg wit="#L" n="bb">is <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
								</app></rdg>
							</app></rdg>
						</app> proprio nisu<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>nisus restitutionis</term>
						</index> se restituit et vibrat, variae autem ob ejus liquiditatem<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>liquiditas</term>
						</index> in eo fiunt vibrationes,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>vibratio aeris</term>
						</index> partium scilicet aliarum majorum aliarum minorum, <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">sed partes mediae<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>pars aeris</term>
							</index></lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">sed</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> eae </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> partes mediae <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> quarum magnitudo talis est, ut simul vibrent cum chorda,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>chorda vibrans</term>
						</index> eae in vibratione perserverant, reliquarum vibrationes destruuntur;<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>pars aeris</term>
						</index> et hae similiter vibrationem<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>vibratio aeris</term>
						</index> suam propagant in alias vicinas,<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>propagatio vibrationis</term>
						</index> et ita porro, usque ad aurem.<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>auris</term>
						</index> In aure <pb type="L"/><app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">autem potest fieri, ut vel <app type="Cfootnote" from="#LH_37_01_016v_tymp-1" to="#LH_37_01_016v_tymp-2">
							<lem type="main"/>
							<note type="lemma-abbrev">tympanum <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/> allapsi</note>
							<note type="editorial">Siehe zu dieser Auffassung der Funktion des Trommelfells etwa H. <hi rendition="#k">Fabri</hi>, <hi rendition="#i">Physica</hi>, tract. III, lib. II, prop. 52 (Bd. II, Lyon 1670, S. 152b–153a)<bibl corresp="#bib_00044">. Eine ähnliche Überlegung findet sich auch in <bibl corresp="#bib_00087">J. <hi rendition="#k">Rohault</hi>, <hi rendition="#i">Traité de physique</hi>, partie I, chap. 26, § 48 (2. Ausgabe, Paris 1672, Bd. I, S. 290).</bibl></bibl></note>
							</app>tympanum<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016v_tymp-1"/><index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>tympanum</term>
							</index> ipsum</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">autem</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> possunt in ipso tympan </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> potest fieri, ut vel tympanum ipsum <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> varie intendamus pro ratione soni allapsi,<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016v_tymp-2"/><index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>sonus allapsus</term>
						</index> vel ut tympanum<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tympanum</term>
						</index> ex diversae tensionis<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>tensio</term>
						</index> constet partibus, quarum aliae ab hoc, aliae ab alio sono<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>sonus allapsus</term>
						</index> <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">pulsentur ut</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">pulsentur</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> . Et hoc modo </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> ut <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> chordae chordis unisonis<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>chorda unisona</term>
						</index> pulsatis<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>chorda pulsata</term>
						</index> consonant<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>chorda consonans</term>
						</index> etsi non nisi ab aere pulsentur.<anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_abschnitt_3-2"/></p>
					<p xml:id="Ch1.p15">Videndum an verum sit, et ex <anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_abschnitt_4-1"/><app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">his demonstrari queat,</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">his</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> demonstretur </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> demonstrari queat, <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> quod omnis sonus<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>sonus</term>
						</index> feratur <anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016v_Schallgeschwindigkeit-1"/><app type="Cfootnote">
						<lem type="main">uniformi velocitate,<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>velocitas uniformis</term>
							</index><index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>velocitas soni</term>
							</index> seu ut celeritas<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>celeritas soni</term>
							</index> sit in ratione distantiarum,<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>distantia</term>
							</index><anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016v_Schallgeschwindigkeit-2"/></lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">uniformi <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/> distantiarum</note>
						<note type="editorial">Leibniz äußert sich hier widersprüchlich. Siehe für eine angemessene Darstellung der gleichförmigen Geschwindigkeit der Schallausbreitung vielmehr G. W. <hi rendition="#k">Leibniz</hi>, Brief an G. C. Schelhammer vom Februar/März 1681 (<hi rendition="#i">LSB</hi> III, 3 N. 182, S. 359.14–360.1) sowie hier unten, N. <ref corresp="L_section_121.xml#N.12.1"/>, S. <ref corresp="L_section_121.xml#LH_37_01_019r_gleichscnell-1"/>.</note>
						</app> et hoc verum puto, prorsus ac si elateria<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term>elaterium</term>
						</index> similia in <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">longam seriem disposita<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>series elateriorum</term>
							</index> sese ordine<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term>ordo</term>
							</index> liberent</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">longam</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> distantiam se </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> seriem disposita <app>
							<rdg wit="#L" n="a">se mutuo liberent </rdg>
							<rdg wit="#L" n="b">sese ordine liberent <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
							</app></rdg>
						</app> [<hi rendition="#i">danach gestrichen und abbrechend:</hi>] <hi rendition="#smaller">vel pulsent. Si <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">chordae<index indexName="Sachen">
							<term><hi rendition="#smaller">chorda parallela</hi></term>
							</index> parallelae</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">chordae</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> vi </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> parallelae <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> eodem modo tensae<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term><hi rendition="#smaller">chorda tensa</hi></term>
						</index> sint numero quotcunque, et una pulsata<index indexName="Sachen">
						<term><hi rendition="#smaller">chorda pulsata</hi></term>
						</index> aliam <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">pulset; aliae consonant;</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">pulset;</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> <formula xml:id="Ch1.p15.m1">
							<m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline">
								<m:mo stretchy="false">⟨</m:mo>
							</m:math>
							</formula>nec<formula xml:id="Ch1.p15.m2">
							<m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline">
								<m:mo stretchy="false">⟩</m:mo>
							</m:math>
							</formula> </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> pulsando <app>
							<rdg wit="#L" n="a">aliquid </rdg>
							<rdg wit="#L" n="b">aliquid </rdg>
							</app></rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="3"> manifestum est </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="4"> aliae consonant; <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> <anchor xml:id="LH_37_01_016r_abschnitt_4-2"/></hi></p>
